title: TVS Motor rolls out black edition of TVS Apache RTR 160 series at Rs 1.09 lakh
description: TVS Motor launches 'A Blaze of Black' Dark edition of TVS Apache 160 RTR at Rs 1,09,990. Vimal Sumbly, Head Business-Premium, emphasizes the brand's 5.5 million global enthusiasts.
